<h2>Chapter 8: The 90-Day SEO Roadmap Template &#123;#ch8&#125;</h2>
<p>Here is the actual template. Copy it into Notion, Asana, ClickUp, or a spreadsheet. Assign owners. Set dates. Run it for 90 days and you will see ranking movement by week 8, clicks growth by week 10, and conversion impact by week 12.</p>
